Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.77,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}也加快了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:14.67,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}秋色的雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:24.39,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}輕撫臉頰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:30.34,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}是你的髮絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.76,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此惹人憐愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.29,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}如此令人傷懷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:49.15,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我不願與你分離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:17:00.35,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}我在追尋 渴望找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:06.12,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}那無形無影之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:12.09,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}人們總擅長展現自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:18.73,ED-CN,,30,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\bord1\blur5\fs45}記憶太過遙遠 就像大海一般
